Blinksale,is,a,web,application,that,allows,professionals,and,small,businesses,to,send,invoices,on,the,Web,Users,can,create,invoices,from,a,template,or,choose,to,customize,the,design,The,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Blinksale,to,work,with,other,applications,in,thier,business,workflow,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML